title: HP MSA 2040: Disk Health Status
agents: hp_msa
catalog: hw/storagehw/hp
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the number of disks and the health states of all disks
 of a HP MSA 2040 storage system. To make it work you have to configure
 the hp_msa datasource program the via WATO.

 If the states of all disks are "OK" then the service state is OK.
 Otherwise the service shows the health status and reason of the disks
 which are not "OK" and changes to WARN or CRIT.

inventory:
 One service is created.
